{# Official-website link with a "leaving our site" courtesy. Expects `nation`. #}
<div class="card">
  <h3>The nation's own website</h3>
  {% if nation.website %}
  <p>For current Chief and Council, membership, programs, and contacts, use the nation's own website, which is the authority: <a href="{{ nation.website }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ nation.website_label }}</a>.</p>
  <p class="muted">You are leaving this member resource. That link opens {{ nation.name }}'s own website, which we do not run or control.</p>
  {% else %}
  <p>{{ nation.website_note }}</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
